summary:
@chrishannah@fosstodon.org I couldn’t agree more. You’ve put your finger on something that’s been bugging me for a while.

The most difficult interactions I’ve had with colleagues have come ultimately from a lack of writing, thinking video calls or in-person chats could cover everything.

On top of your bullet points at the end of your article, I find when things are written down, in a place where they will live longer than a Slack thread, it’s easier to ensure everyone is on the same page.
